[I] A lightweight Virtual Machine Manager (VMM)

[T] Hyperlight is a lightweight Virtual Machine Manager (VMM) designed to be
[T] embedded within applications. It enables safe execution of untrusted code
[T] within micro virtual machines with very low latency and minimal overhead.

[U] https://github.com/hyperlight-dev/hyperlight

